    "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nThe current build pipeline combines many heavy steps into a single sequence \r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/NVIDIA/spark-rapids/blob/23bf5ca2555cc8cc880e243a1645b2606445e85e/jenkins/spark-nightly-build.sh#L27\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/NVIDIA/spark-rapids/blob/cdee7f3051163f928a4af7e7aa8a297368b45614/jenkins/spark-premerge-build.sh#L40\r\n\r\nMoreover we skip tests for every other MAINTENANCE version, these steps don't require GPU nodes and can be separated  into containers running on vanilla nodes.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nadd a parallel stage for every shim build with the minimum necessary requirements for containers\r\n\r\n**Describe alternatives you've considered**\r\nA clear and concise description of any alternative solutions or features you've considered.\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\n#3523 ",
